            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S. T.) Placuit atque convenit inter Borningum fq. Opizonis nec non et Azo
                        fq. Rozani ut debeat dare sicut in presenti dedit ipse Borningum eidem Azoni
                        ad fictum reddendum <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellario
                            nomine</rs> usque ad annos XXIX expletos <rs key="#Petiae">pecias duas
                            de terra</rs> una est cum <rs key="#Forests">bosco</rs> alia est <rs
                            key="#Cereals">aratoria</rs> iuris <rs key="#Monasteries">mon.</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53" key="#Monasteries">S.Sixti</orgName> et
                            <rs key="#Feudum">feodum</rs> ipsius Borningi, que sunt posite ultra <rs
                            key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs> Padi in <placeName ref="#places/1936"
                            >Sanguineto</placeName> et in Roncalie non multum longe da la Turre, ea
                        racione ut per eum terre meliorenture et persolvere exinde debead singulis
                        annis <rs key="#Rent_in_money">fictum den bonorum cone IV</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/43" key="#Cities">Placencia</placeName> a casa
                        abitacionis ipsius Opizonis. <rs key="#Penalty">Pena: sol. centum argenti
                            den. bon. Cone.</rs> An. Incarn. MCVI, V die mensis imarii, ind. XV.
                        Act. in civitate Placencia. S.m. iamscripti Borningi. SS.mm. Alberti da
                        Revegozo et Petri filii Martini Ledani seu item Borningi Grapella atque
                        Cunizoni tt. (S.T) Gezo <rs key="#Notary">not</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
